    public final class RamAccountingTermsEnum
extends org.apache.lucene.index.FilteredTermsEnum
    TermsEnum that takes a MemoryCircuitBreaker, increasing the breaker every time .next(...) is called. Proxies all methods to the original TermsEnum otherwise.
